.IX Subsection "CMS and PKCS#7 updates"
.IP "\(bu" 4
Added CAdES-BES signature verification support.
.IP "\(bu" 4
Added CAdES-BES signature scheme and attributes support (\s-1RFC 5126\s0) to \s-1CMS API.\s0
.IP "\(bu" 4
